data.description: Wonderful home in the Brightwood Farm neighborhood that has all the recreational amenities! Neighborhood clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, grill and picnic area. LVP flooring downstairs. Vaulted entry. Kitchen has granite countertops, stone backsplash, island, pantry, double oven, breakfast area and open into the living room! Living room has gas FP. Half bath and laundry room on main level. Upstairs you have the primary bedroom with a walk in closet; bathroom with a dual vanity, separate shower and a garden tub. 2nd and 3rd bedroom at the end of the hall. 4th bedroom is large and could be used as a bedroom or bonus room. Backyard is fenced and has a patio with a gazebo that conveys.
